==Scottish Gaelic==

===Etymology===
Old Irish [[oc]]

===Preposition===
'''aig'''

# [[at]], [[by]], [[near]], close by
#* aig an taigh
#** at the house
#* aig baile
#** at home
# in possession
#* bha aig duine àraidh dithis mhac
#** a certain man had two sons
# on account of
#* aig meud aigheir
#** on account of his excessive joy
# [[for]]
# [[on]]

